Package fi.abo.kogni.soile2.utils

Interface MessageResponseHandler

All Known Implementing Classes:
MessageResponseHandlerImpl
public interface MessageResponseHandler
A Handler for default Replies to the context. Assumes, that the response type is simple text or Json and will answer the context accordingly Does nothing if not successfull.
Author:
Thomas Pfau
